<font color="#E767E7">(GUNFlRE)</font>

02:12:56.602 --> 02:12:58.436
<font color="#E767E7">(PEOPLE CHEERING)</font>

02:14:04.420 --> 02:14:06.587
<font color="#808080">HANS</font>: So when the military
history of this night is written,

02:14:06.672 --> 02:14:10.341
