02:27:21.424 --> 02:27:22.800
<font color="#E767E7">(GUNSHOT)</font>

02:27:23.927 --> 02:27:25.427
Scalp Hermann.

02:27:27.096 --> 02:27:28.764
Are you mad?

02:27:29.140 --> 02:27:30.891
What have you done?

02:27:31.392 --> 02:27:34.728
