that deal you made with the brass.

02:27:51.371 --> 02:27:53.121
End the war tonight?

02:27:54.541 --> 02:27:56.083
I'd make that deal.

02:27:56.167 --> 02:27:58.001
How about you, Utivich?
You make that deal?

02:27:58.086 --> 02:27:59.086
